{"tid":575890,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"大台珍貴文革紀錄片被刪重post，請廣傳！","createTime":"2018-02-28T12:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T07:33:40.000Z","uid":63183,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"38a5ec10c0903c6d199c8ee43f8e71525e231ef6","tid":575890,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/205929_b7a1fc54cdd2a0d0fee78e20d020e021.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F205929_b7a1fc54cdd2a0d0fee78e20d020e021.png&h=6f4d6633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前我整理錄影帶搵到二十幾年前，大台拍攝嘅紀錄片《文革三十年》，就隨手放上Youtube Channel，無諗到大受歡迎，仲受到８５２郵報推介，簡介如下：<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/157548/%E3%80%90%E6%96%87%E9%9D%A950%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%91%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB20%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%80-%E6%AF%9B%E6%BE%A4%E6%9D%B1%E8%BF%91%E8%BA%AB%E7%A7%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F157548%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%2587%25E9%259D%25A950%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB20%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E3%2580%2580-%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25BF%2591%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%25A7%2598%2F&d=g96y2tAFGhmrj%2B%2FMFxWKGy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1ceee4bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/157548/%E3%80%90%E6%96%87%E9%9D%A950%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%91%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB20%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%80-%E6%AF%9B%E6%BE%A4%E6%9D%B1%E8%BF%91%E8%BA%AB%E7%A7%98/</a><br />\n<br />\n「在1996年文革爆發30年之際，主權移交前夕的香港，無綫電視就製作過一連五輯的文革專題報道，分別為「火紅歲月」、「造反有理」、「血色山河」、「上山下鄉」及「革命烙印」，詳細解釋文革發生的原因、過程及結果。<br />\n<br />\n當時的節目主持為李汶靜，特輯收集了大量歷史圖片和影片，用旁白加訪問的模式，按時序向觀眾梳理文化大革命。<br />\n<br />\n專輯的第一集「火紅歲月」，解釋文化大革命發生的原因。節目的受訪者，包括於50年代擔任毛澤東秘書的李銳、長時間做毛澤東保健醫生的王鶴斌以及從小受毛澤東思想熏陶，並參與過文革的紅衛兵。節目通過講述他們對毛澤東的個人了解，側面解釋為何毛澤東會發動文化大革命。」<br />\n<br />\n但無諗到喺習近平大權在握，即將稱帝之際，我個頻道俾唔知咩人投訴停權，為咗令到大家有得睇返，我另外開咗個youtube channel up返成套片上去：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmWJsRR7_8M5vGwdpiWo-bGVB0S9VhibE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLmWJsRR7_8M5vGwdpiWo-bGVB0S9VhibE&d=g96y2tAFGhmrj%2B%2FMFxWKGy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a833eba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmWJsRR7_8M5vGwdpiWo-bGVB0S9VhibE</a><br />\n<br />\n因為死channel變咗好多本來已經ｓｈａｒｅ我條片嘅各地網站都死晒ｌｉｎｋ，希望各位有識之士幫手share返條片，唔好比呢啲珍貴嘅紀錄片失傳！多謝！"},{"pid":"68955e4568ed8b185459f13f5a5d738790136d7e","tid":575890,"uid":48796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:10:59.000Z","msg":"古董要分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d409541a87b42769790feb03cc9cb3f49a72a84","tid":575890,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6a80e8c520c69171ee2ed3a3d00faf54eddeab","tid":575890,"uid":90166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"可唔可以upload上google drive我再download"},{"pid":"a32965a2e49ba5bb8538e4e7069c0775ab087e56","tid":575890,"uid":63183,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da6a80e8c520c69171ee2ed3a3d00faf54eddeab","tid":575890,"uid":90166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"可唔可以upload上google drive我再download"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1fben8WnKUr6yaCFkGHnblsaMy_wrfDgE?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F